9
00:02:18,110 --> 00:02:20,110
 You may not know...

10
00:02:20,110 --> 00:02:23,180
 but your destiny is being written even at this very moment.

11
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:25,780

12
00:02:25,780 --> 00:02:28,150
 By the hand of god.

13
00:02:37,690 --> 00:02:40,730

