 Kang Young Min will prepare a surprise event

15
00:02:51,700 --> 00:02:57,700
 for his girlfriend this weekend afternoon on a subway line 1 train.

16
00:02:59,030 --> 00:03:03,540
 If your romance always starts fresh

17
