00:03:31,050 --> 00:03:35,810
 this is how we write human beings' destinies every day.

25
00:03:35,810 --> 00:03:38,280
 The two gods you were introduced to earlier

26
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:41,580
 and this one in front of me, too.

27
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:50,870
Damn it, I can't stand this.

28
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:53,310
- Who are you so obsessed with? 
 - Jeong Ba Reum.

29
00:03:53,310 --> 00:03:56,340
The most unique one among the destinies I write.

30
00:03:56,340 --> 00:03:58,200
I'm going to make a masterpiece out of it.

31
00:03:58,200 --> 00:04:02,070
My goodness! My lord! You're here!

32
00:04:02,070 --> 00:04:03,760
Hello.

33
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:06,900
Did she say "lord?" To you? Right now?

34
00:04:06,900 --> 00:04:08,730
You don't know that the landlord is more powerful than the creator God?

35
00:04:08,730 --> 00:04:12,050
He is our landlord.

36
00:04:12,050 --> 00:04:13,670
Oh, do you go to church by chance?

37
00:04:13,670 --> 00:04:17,050
Then sorry. I'll find another nickname.

38
