Are you sure she is joking?

39
00:04:20,330 --> 00:04:23,370
Rent is a lot cheaper in this building than in the one next door.

40
00:04:23,370 --> 00:04:25,480
On top of that, business is good here, too.

41
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,970
She says the landlord usually kicks them out if that is the case

42
00:04:27,970 --> 00:04:29,160
because they want to run the business themselves.

43
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:31,710
And it's not that she knows who you are?

44
00:04:31,710 --> 00:04:34,200
