143
00:12:17,590 --> 00:12:18,510
How's the business? Good?

144
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:21,800
Yes, very good. But it could always be better.

145
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:23,950
I'm still raising a baby over here.

146
00:12:23,950 --> 00:12:25,900
You are always so funny.

147
00:12:25,900 --> 00:12:27,930
But who is this?

148
00:12:27,930 --> 00:12:30,440
Oh! Must be your youngest sister.

149
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:33,060
- You are beautiful, just like your sister.
 - Oh, stop.

150
00:12:33,060 --> 00:12:37,150
- See you later. 
